flowchart TB
    subgraph Client
        U([User]) --> API[FastAPI]
    end

    subgraph Ingestion
        API -- POST /ingest --> ING[Ingest Service]
        ING --> PDF[PDF Reader] --> CHK[Chunker] --> EMB[Embedder]
